le":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为啥各个回答的评论区会冒出来这么多喷答主的？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e稍微对数学/民科了解一点的话都知道这些回答一点都不过分，那么这个问题怎么吸引来的这么多对这些丝毫没有了解过的人？\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003emdzz，知乎开始给我推送一大堆这样的答案了，真的服气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以数学就是这样的东西，经常看到做数学的答主只要表现出了一点“高中及以下的数学很简单”的意思，评论区就会冒出来玻璃心——连我都学不会的东西，怎么能说他这么简单呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然一种是认为它难，一种是认为它简单，但是本质上是相同的——数学过于普及，以至于几乎所有人都认为自己可以评判一番，然而绝大多数人看不到甚至没法想象到数学的难度所在。这是真的可悲。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561476436,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c26a5be5e96c8baad325d387057cadc9","url_token":"qing-zhi-34-60-40","name":"青稚","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d36df666ad312eddeaad5dc593614ab_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0d36df666ad312eddeaad5dc593614ab_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c26a5be5e96c8baad325d387057cadc9","user_type":"people","headline":"梦里一碗青稞酒接过","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561476436","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545970810,"updated_time":1545970810,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我想问问，证明哥猜之前，你知道（1+1）、（1+2）、1+1、1+2的区别吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果不能\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e麻烦把高等数学和初等数论做满分学几个专业词汇再考虑考虑报考新闻与传播学院\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这等人才学数学真是白瞎\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你应该研究热搜的算法，那才是你的天地\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS：知乎用户不比微博，有真材实料的人多了去了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePPS：我看到题主在一条回答里说“我不敢说我的证明是没有问题的”这句话让我觉得你真的是一个很好的人，思维也很好，但是，我不想鼓励你是因为我看了你的回答，河北大学数学系的相关你要百度？连给招生办校办打电话的意识都没有？开一个数学专栏你什么都不写？问国际上发表数学论文的地方？你的论文不用百度有道你能写几个单词？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在觉得你连陈景润先生都论文有几页都不知道\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许你有那个能力，但是，你的格局让你别说在清北，随便一个211你都待不下去\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562265884,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aeb0f9b12d3274d2ff548969ad591dde","url_token":"why-jiang","name":"扒饭的why酱","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/b815eb44d47638ac69040058e3eff619_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/b815eb44d47638ac69040058e3eff619_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aeb0f9b12d3274d2ff548969ad591dde","user_type":"people","headline":"宅男/ACG爱好者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562265884","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546069208,"updated_time":1546069208,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e公司最近上市了，估值三百亿，请问各位午餐泡面是加蛋好还是加肠好？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561171073,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"afd9cba45786d54c33c5593a2c32a4ce","url_token":"luo-xiao-sheng-38","name":"罗笑生","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3d7d64110ee8a5f736c84feb8e059090_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3d7d64110ee8a5f736c84feb8e059090_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/afd9cba45786d54c33c5593a2c32a4ce","user_type":"people","headline":"为了不一样而不一样","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false}