vg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1079'%20height='902'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1079\" data-rawheight=\"902\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c6c14640ba48e651b4bb7c19be91c90f_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1079\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-654fcf8ddccb7be880b84b9cdcafa483_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-654fcf8ddccb7be880b84b9cdcafa483_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560982793,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6e9610306638d2a49c38cd054dd3c3e","url_token":"zhao-qing-xi-74","name":"夜幕灰尘","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4524946e80d93381d882c8307b4c0dbe_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4524946e80d93381d882c8307b4c0dbe_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6e9610306638d2a49c38cd054dd3c3e","user_type":"people","headline":"人生多愁，岂能无酒","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560982793","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545904368,"updated_time":1545904368,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e各位答主请慎言\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主很有可能已经被系统附体，而歌猜只是题主的一个小任务而已，我估计题主以后还会狂揽诺贝尔奖十三次，菲儿兹奖三次，而且会建立数学大一统纲领。并且会陆续攻克核聚变商用，去火星亲自寻找生命等等等等\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真的，题主未来的成就无法预估！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559989388,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"387c4238372b4c50ad5ef3125434a5c1","url_token":"jin-tian-yi-12-83","name":"金田一","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-249309645c0ce7b3a524e9861b1e4a25_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-249309645c0ce7b3a524e9861b1e4a25_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/387c4238372b4c50ad5ef3125434a5c1","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559989388","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545799583,"updated_time":1545799854,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e老实说，不太可能。就高中生最多初等数论的水平是不可能完成的任务。当然如果你真的证明成功，别说清华北大学生，MIT哈佛牛津剑桥教授任你挑，并且下个菲尔兹奖，沃尔夫奖都是你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e补充一点，我高中同学用了一节数学课的时间声称自己证明了费马大定理，考虑到他的数学水平（没有其他意思他文科很好）我委婉的告诉他可能有错误，结果非得给我看，我一看，嗯除了一开始的证明写对了，其他的好像全错，，，\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562859753,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","url_token":"virbianium","name":"而后 乃今培风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","user_type":"people","headline":"一个想成为理论物理学家，也知道自己可能在做梦但为之奋斗的青年。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562859753","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546154647,"updated_time":1546154647,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e答主和题主有点像，也想考清北。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说大多数人物理天赋是1.0，那我可能在1.5~2.0之间，IPhO、APhO国家队应该有3.0+，而且他们还刻苦训练。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e读了高中，知道了五大竞赛这回事。仗着初中物理水平压某一线城市的二，三线初中全级同学一头，兴冲冲地入了坑，发现连入门级的物竞题都做不出来。经过这几个月的学习下来，我总算是懂了点皮毛。而且总结出一个规律。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e高考是通向好大学的最快最简单最轻松途径。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e像竞赛这种，检测单科水平的比赛，许多人认为那是捷径，其实不然，它需要的综合水平，比高考更高。而参加竞赛去了清北的，90%以上都是能裸分清北的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只有真正接触过竞赛的，才会明白竞赛党的苦和累，还有竞赛的难。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有学习数学物理之路的漫长。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前路是一座又一座山。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而证明哥德巴赫猜想，其难度比竞赛更高百倍，这更不是种捷径，是一个无底洞。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他会吞掉你无穷无尽的时间，无穷无尽的精力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是种赌博，不要投入太多在里面，避免毁灭性的失败。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的和哥德巴赫猜想有不解之缘，想去北大清华只是流于表面的原因，那么还是选择扎扎实实学好课内知识，考上一所好的大学，努力提升自己的数学水平，等到水平真的达到那种境界的时候，再专攻哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能明年的CPhO预赛都过不去的准物竞选手如实说：）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559484572,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bc69ae3d61094819255baa678f3bfc94","url_token":"hong-ji-lei","name":"蜉蝣叕撼树","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bc69ae3d61094819255baa678f3bfc94","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559484572","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545731161,"updated_time":1545731161,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你有这本事还不如参加竞赛来的实际。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你想到用证明哥猜的方式进名校，大概率应该是你硬考考不上吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你硬靠考不上，也就是竞赛题大概率也是搞不定的了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e常规的大多数人都能学明白的高考应试知识和一部分人能学明白的竞赛，你都搞不定，你凭什么就认为你能搞定全世界最优秀的数学家都搞不定的问题？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562304623,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9193cc34d9d0ef90ba61146873814523","url_token":"xu-chang-qin-68","name":"一曲流苏叙韶华","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-906f749f3f780f0e3e0b0a03aa96324e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-906f749f3f780f0e3e0b0a03aa96324e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9193cc34d9d0ef90ba61146873814523","user_type":"people","headline":"年少坏事做尽，老来嫉恶如仇。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562304623","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546072738,"updated_time":1546072738,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果可以证明哥德巴赫猜想，清北复交常青藤随你挑，不过不是去当学生，是去做教授。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560766335,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","he