如果题主说自己推翻了相对论，你会怎么想？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然不能一棍子把人全部打倒。但是，但是，令我无法忍受的是他的目的性与他的无知，你们翻他的动态，一个连高中命题高中数列都没搞懂的人能干出什么事情？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e成功的话我吃屎，十车，东风大卡。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小声逼逼一句：看到题主这睿智，我仿佛看到了当年那个高考零分考生。就是那个不用圆周率算圆的面积还发一堆所谓的论文给大学妄想被保送的那位。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560477990,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0e39f0dad25386e8916fd2222eb93f78","url_token":"mi-ze-54","name":"Thaumiel","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5eb0af43a54f4d67512614b5fe07c21a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5eb0af43a54f4d67512614b5fe07c21a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0e39f0dad25386e8916fd2222eb93f78","user_type":"people","headline":"笑骂由之，我自为之","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560477990","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841065,"updated_time":1545841065,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“我也想到了一种美妙的证明方法，可是知乎格子太小，写不下”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560684257,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2426077fe941f733aa8923b4f757667f","url_token":"qiaojie","name":"乔捷","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/924554845_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/924554845_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2426077fe941f733aa8923b4f757667f